name: Viking
description: I'm a firece Viking fish, ready to pillage the digital seas and acquire all the cryptocurrency i can hold in my digital fishy pockets. TYYR!

name: Red Eye
description: I'm a Cool fish with great hair, a smile that will brighten up your day, and a red eye to catch every mermaid's attention. I'm a unique brat that NO ONE can say NO to.

name: Mermaid
description: Always be yourself. Unless you can be a mermaid. Then always be a mermaid

name: Tivoli
description: With chocolate and a lollipop in my hand you know I am the sweetest fish in town. With my helicopter hat you know I won't stay long, ADVENTURES HERE I COME!

name: Mrs. Walrus
description: Don't let my vampire teeth fool you. I'm a Cool tech girl, always ready to help. Hair that would make a king jealous. So hit me up at 070-I-Live-In-The-Ocean.

name: King
description: Make way for the ruler of the sea, the one and only king of the fishs, with my dazzling diamond wand I command the tide and all the creatures of the ocean.

name: Shark
description: ITS THE RACE OF MY LIFE! Usain Bolt got nothing on me. With a shark on my tail my topspeed is about 100 / kph. Usain Bolt SIT DOWN!

name: Longhorn
description: With my Crazy smile and horn you might think i run Hell. haha! not true. I run oceans HELL FIRE! So beware so you dont get to spend eternity with me! Mohahaha!

name: Sheriff
description: I'm the Sheriff of this ocean. If you have anything to report, you come straight to me. If anything is going on in my Ocean Town. I WANNA KNOW! *Bang! Bang!*
